    {
        "id": "QC2ZDHSXW4XPXT32COYQPCTV",
        "name": "Custom 3D Printed Hard Carry Case with Handle",
        "description": "Our 3D Printed Hard Carry Case with Handle is a lightweight, durable storage solution designed and custom-made in-house. Crafted using high-quality filament, this case combines strength, portability, and the versatility of 3D printing for a unique, functional product. Perfect for organizing tools, electronics, gaming accessories, or personal items, this 3D printed hard case offers practical storage with a modern, custom-made twist. Dimensions of the box - External 230x208x81mm Internal 220x150x75mm\n\n\u2705 Durable Construction: Strong shell design to protect your items during storage or travel\n\u2705 Ergonomic Handle: Easy-to-grip handle for convenient carrying anywhere\n\u2705 Lightweight & Compact: Designed for everyday use without added bulk\n\u2705\u00a0Custom Options Available:\u00a0Brand-able with your Company Name and/or Logo, and choice of color(s). \n\ud83d\udce9 Provide your preferred contact info in the notes at checkout or email your logo / design to us at morgan3dokc@gmail.com.\n\ud83d\udce6 Made in the USA by Morgan 3D Prints \u2013 Local pickup or shipping anywhere in the U.S.",
        "category": "Custom",
