        "url": null,
        "priceCents": 5000
    },
    {
        "id": "KENVNSSQ3XCO2HC6OZPH4GPT",
        "name": "3D Printed Purse Silk Purple with Disco Ball Effect",
        "description": "Step into the future of fashion with our 3D Printed Purse, Silk Purple, featuring a Disco Ball Effect. Combining cutting-edge 3D printing technology with a sleek, modern aesthetic, this purse is lightweight, durable, and a true conversation piece.\n\u2705  Disco Ball Look: Unique textured filament creates a high-end reflective appearance\n\u2705 3D Printed Construction: Precision-printed for durability and a clean, professional finish\n\u2705 Lightweight & Strong: Perfect for everyday use without added bulk\n\u2705 Eco-Friendly Production: Made to reduce waste and promote sustainable fashion\nWhether you\u2019re looking to stand out at an event or add a futuristic touch to your wardrobe, this 3D printed purse is the perfect blend of style and innovation. This bag is structured and will stand up on it's own, even when completely empty. The strap is fully adjustable and removable if you prefer to use your own strap. The Bag is 6 inches tall x 6 inches wide x 3 inches deep.\n\ud83d\udce6 Made in the USA by Morgan 3D Prints \u2013 Local pickup or shipping anywhere in the U.S.",
