    {
        "id": "AQ3H2FZ3S36QWW3IFD4FH4ZI",
        "name": "Teeny Tiny Weed Tote (PRE-ROLL SIZED)",
        "description": "Bring big vibes in a small package with our 3D Printed \u201cTeeny Tiny Weed Tote\u201d. This miniature cannabis-themed tote is perfect for holding small items, displaying as a novelty piece, or gifting to any cannabis enthusiast. Size: Pre-roll sized (approx. 100mm wide x 55mm deep x 40mm tall). Whether used to stash small accessories, as a desk decoration, or as a fun conversation starter, this 3D printed \u201cTeeny Tiny Weed Tote\u201d is a must-have novelty piece.\n\u2705 Miniature Tote Design: A fun, playful twist on a classic weed bag\n\u2705 3D Printed Construction: Durable, lightweight, and made with high-quality filament\n\u2705 Compact & Portable: Small enough to fit in your pocket or use as a display piece\n\u2705 Custom Options Available:\u00a0Brand-able with your Company Name and/or Logo, and choice of color(s) when ordered in bulk ONLY. ALL SINGLE UNIT ORDERS WILL BE SHIPPED AS PICTURED.\n\u2705 Perfect Gift: Great for smokers, collectors, or anyone who loves cannabis culture with a sense of humor\n\ud83d\udce6 Made in the USA by Morgan 3D Prints\u2013 Local pickup or shipping anywhere in the U.S.",
