    },
    {
        "id": "CRPEO3CZHTZJUOONDG4MMFWV",
        "name": "Custom 3D Printed Logo Lightbox \u2013 Die-Cut LED Display Sign",
        "description": "Show off your brand with a Custom 3D Printed Logo Lightbox \u2014 designed to feature your logo or design in glowing, illuminated detail. Perfect for small businesses, content creators, event booths, and home studios, this die-cut lightbox blends branding and art into one standout display.\n\u2705 Fully Customizable: We turn your logo or artwork into a bold, precision-cut faceplate\n\u2705 Durable PLA Frame & Panel: Made with high-quality 3D printing filament for long-lasting use\n\u2705 LED-Ready: 30mm Depth Compatible with LED strip lighting (not included)\n\u2705 Display Anywhere: Wall-mountable (or free-standing depending on your design) for versatile placement\n\u2705 Made-to-Order: Choose your colors, size, and design for a truly unique sign\nWhether you\u2019re branding your pop-up booth, lighting up your office, or creating one-of-a-kind wall d\u00e9cor, this illuminated sign is a powerful way to get noticed.\n\ud83d\udce9 Provide your preferred contact info in the notes at checkout or email your logo / design to us at morgan3dokc@gmail.com.\n\ud83d\udce6 Made in the USA by Morgan 3D Prints \u2013 Local pickup or shipping anywhere in the U.S.",
