    {
        "id": "HNWLTJRBP5B6YU3OX2LZVFW5",
        "name": "Custom 3D Printed LED Signs \u2013 Personalized Die-Cut Logo & Text Displays",
        "description": "Stand out with a Custom 3D Printed LED Sign designed to showcase your logo, brand, or text in glowing detail. Each sign is die-cut to match your design and built with an LED-ready interior for stunning backlighting. Perfect for businesses, barber shops, gaming setups, events, and personal d\u00e9cor.\n\u2705 Fully Customizable: Send us your logo, text, or design\u2014we\u2019ll bring it to life\n\u2705 Die-Cut 3D Design: Unlike flat signs, your logo is cut to shape for maximum impact\n\u2705 LED Backlit Ready: Designed to fit LED puck or strip lighting (not included)\n\u2705 Durable 3D Printed Build: Lightweight yet strong, crafted with premium filament\n\u2705 Perfect for Business & Home: Eye-catching for shops, booths, studios, or gaming rooms\n\u2705 Custom Sizes Available: From desktop-size signs to large wall branding pieces\nWhether you need bold shop signage or unique personalized d\u00e9cor, our LED-ready custom signs make a powerful statement day and night.\n\ud83d\udce6 Made in the USA by Morgan 3D \u2013 Local pickup or shipping anywhere in the U.S.\n\ud83d\udca1 LED lighting not included \u2013 fits standard LED strips.\n\ud83d\udce9 Provide your preferred contact info in the notes at checkout or email your logo / design to us at morgan3dokc@gmail.com.\nAvailable Sizes:\nSmall Letters (Approx. 4 inches wide each)\n$6 - $12 Per Letter\nPerfect for desks, shelves, and small displays. Great for personal d\u00e9cor or creator branding.\nMedium (Approx. 6 inches wide each)\n$7 - $14 Per Letter\nIdeal for small businesses, barber shops, or event booths. Big enough to grab attention without overpowering.\nLarge (Approx. 8 inches wide each)\n$12 - $24 Per Letter\nPremium indoor shop signage. Great for storefronts, wall art, or professional branding displays.",
