    {
        "id": "WHSA5YM6WEJGITJ7G4HYZCMT",
        "name": "Russian Nesting Totes - Teeny Tiny Tote of Various Sizes",
        "description": "Compact & Portable Design\nBring big vibes in a small package with our 3D Printed \u201cTeeny Tiny Totes\u201d. These miniature totes are perfect for holding small items, displaying as a novelty piece, or gifting to any miniature enthusiast. Whether used to stash small accessories, as a desk decoration, or as a fun conversation starter, this 3D printed \u201cTeeny Tiny Tote\u201d is a must-have novelty piece.\nDurable & Lightweight Construction\nThe construction of the \u201cTeeny Tiny Tote\u201d is durable, lightweight, and made with high-quality filament. It's a fun, playful twist on the classic 3D Printed design. This compact and portable tote fits easily in your pocket or can be used as a display piece. Enjoy its functionality and style in a small, manageable size.",
