        "name": "Slurm Soda Can \u2013 Futurama Inspired 3D Printed Wall Art",
        "description": "Features vibrant pops of blue, lime, and magenta, reminiscent of the iconic Slurm Can from Futurama.\nThe design is recognizable from the hit show, making it a must-have for fans.\nLightweight PLA Material\nMade from lightweight PLA material, easy to mount or display.\nThe material ensures a lightweight design, making it easy to hang or place anywhere. \ufe0f\nCollector's Favorite\nA must-have for sci-fi fans and lovers of 90s animated classics.\nThis 3D printed Slurm Can adds personality to any room, bringing back memories of the hit show.\nMaterial and Design\nMaterial: Lightweight PLA.\nDesign: Recognizable from the hit show.\n Bold Design Features\n20MM Option shown in pictures.\nDie-Cut Design: Bold silhouette.\n3D Printed Frame & Faceplate: Made with durable, high-quality filament for long-lasting use.\n20mm and 40mm are LED Light Compatible: Designed to house a USB powered LED strip light, NOT INCLUDED.\nVersatile Installation Options\nWall-Mount or Free-Stand options available: Lightweight design makes it easy to hang or place anywhere. Made in the USA by Morgan 3D Prints \u2013 Local pickup or shipping anywhere in the U.S. Enjoy the bold, futuristic display piece today!",
