    {
        "id": "5TZZJACODW43SOH4OVXLS4RT",
        "name": "Complaint Dept Desk Sign \u2013 Take a Number (Funny Grenade Gag Gift)",
        "description": "Add Explosive Humor to Your Space!\nElevate your office decor with the \"Complaint Dept. \u2013 Take a Number\" Desk Sign. This 3D printed sign features a realistic grenade design with a pull-pin number tag. It's the perfect gag gift for coworkers or managers. The bold, easy-to-read lettering ensures visibility. Made by Morgan 3D in OKC, it offers local pickup or shipping across the USA.\nRealistic Details & Durability\nThe sign includes a pull-pin with a \u201cNumber 1\u201d tag, adding a touch of realism. It's lightweight yet durable, crafted for longevity. The high-quality 3D print ensures crisp text and a durable finish. Ideal for home offices, workplaces, or as a fun gift, this sign guarantees a laugh wherever displayed.\nA Conversation Starter\nThis sign is more than just d\u00e9cor; it's a conversation starter. Its unique design catches attention and sparks smiles. Perfect for anyone dealing with complaints, it adds a humorous twist to everyday interactions. Enjoy the attention it brings to your space, making it a standout piece.",
